snippet.title: SUPER 56 Announcement Trailer: Coming to Steam Early Access (PC) 20th February 2023
snippet.description:
Welcome to Hell! Players will be staying with KRONOS and BRONES, two low-ranking demons who just acquired the super-rare retro game SUPER 56. The only problem is they both suck at games so it’s the players job to help them reach Rank S and “rub it everyone’s faces”.

Take on 56 brutal mini-games, compete in daily challenges, get achievements and destroy hi scores in SUPER 56.

Coming 20th February 2023 to Steam.

Download the demo and play today: https://bit.ly/Super56Steam
